142
01:07:54,125 --> 01:07:57,583
<b>An information world does not need to
feel artificial from within.</b>

143
01:07:58,583 --> 01:08:00,208
<b>Its reality comes from the autonomy,</b>

144
01:08:00,833 --> 01:08:04,083
<b>consistency, and cost of its
own internal updates.</b>

145
01:08:05,208 --> 01:08:07,291
<b>The process is real because
the predictions,</b>

146
01:08:07,665 --> 01:08:10,667
<b>records, boundaries, and experiences
