148
01:08:12,916 --> 01:08:14,708
<b>When we look out at the
stars and ask why,</b>

149
01:08:15,291 --> 01:08:17,541
<b>we are asking a question inside
a system that</b>

150
01:08:17,541 --> 01:08:19,733
<b>seems to share our deepest pattern.</b>

151
01:08:20,333 --> 01:08:23,958
<b>It distinguishes, it anticipates,
it verifies, it updates.</b>

152
01:08:25,166 --> 01:08:27,208
<b>Every measurement participates
in the cycle.</b>

153
01:08:28,250 --> 01:08:29,416
<b>Every memory carries it.</b>

154
01:08:29,958 --> 01:08:31,667
<b>Every living system depends on it.</b>

155
01:08:32,166 --> 01:08:33,583
<b>Every question repeats it.</b>

156
01:08:34,291 --> 01:08:37,866
<b>Distinguish, anticipate, verify,
update, continue.</b>


